CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1945, pg. 3, reads: "Dinner Party - A dinner party was given recently at the home of Mrs. Birdie Simmons, in honor of Miss Thelma Eichelberger, who is home from a New York nursing school. Those present were Blanche Mahriney, Myrtle Wood, Birdie Simmons, Geraldine Smith, Thelma Eichelberger and Jean Willis. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six women, including Blanche Mahriney, Myrtle Wood, Birdie Simmons, Geraldine Smith, Thelma Eichelberger, and Jean Willis, posed around floral chair in living room of Simmons home
